          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Subclass and override this method to handle hardware-specific tasks during I/O shutdown, then call the superclass to update the I/O state. The framework expects this call to always succeed or fail.",
